<title>INDIA: POLL-India Bajaj Auto 6-mth net seen down.</title>
<headline>POLL-India Bajaj Auto 6-mth net seen down.</headline>
<dateline>BOMBAY 1997-08-06</dateline>
<text>
<p>Net profit of Indian scooter giant Bajaj Auto Ltd is seen falling 0.9 percent to 2.2 billion rupees in the first half of fiscal 1997/98 (April-March), a Reuter poll consensus of 18 leading brokerages found on Wednesday.</p>
<p>The firm's sales are forecast to slip 8.3 percent to 14.7 billion rupees in the six months to September 30, 1997.</p>
<p>Following are the details of the poll compared with actuals for the first half of 1996/97.</p>
